programme.title: The Illegal Immigrant
programme.desc: This is a gritty and realistic Chinatown tale about the life of a Chinese illegal immigrant and his journey in New York. He is looking for a fake marriage with a girl so as to gain the right of abode there. Despite all the hardships and misfortunes, he tries to cope with life and reach for his dreams.

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xing’s son attempts drug trafficking to save his father’s studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the country’s energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Undercover Hidden Dragon
programme.desc: In this hilarious comedy, Fat is a gangster who suffers from amnesia. Believing that he is actually an undercover policeman, Fat attempts to arrest gang leader Big Bro, but instead becomes the gangsters’ best ally. To complicate matters further, a gangster named Wind, who looks exactly like Fat, starts a turf war with Big Bro.

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover in a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Lost Love
programme.desc: Mei tries to get over the death of her young son by becoming a foster parent. For 13 years, Mei’s dedication to the foster child leads her to neglect her husband and the true needs of the child. It is only through the child’s unintentional help that the couple finally manages to salvage their relationship.

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Daily’s Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: Confinement
programme.desc: Si Ling, a pregnant painter, moves into her dream home after winning an award and hires a confinement nanny. As she begins her one-month confinement after giving birth to her daughter, inexplicable incidents start happening in the house, threatening both her and her baby…

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Hong Kong Hong Kong
programme.desc: After moving to Hong Kong, illegal immigrant Mang has no choice but to live in cramped quarters with male migrants who abuse her. In order to attain Hong Kong residency and a better life, she agrees to marry a lonely old carpenter. After her marriage, Mang crosses paths again with her ex-lover, and the two develop a passionate affair...

programme.title: Love Never Ends
programme.desc: An empty-nest elderly man and a widowed elderly woman who collects scrap, meet unexpectedly and gradually develop feelings for each other. An elderly couple whose wife suffers from a serious illness, makes a living by selling scrap. Both these elderly couples fall deeply in love and prove that love never ends, even if there is no tomorrow!

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The “passion choir pilot program” trains students from three underperforming schools’ choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition. While it seems impossible, a renowned conductor, Yim Tsz Long, unexpectedly agrees to lead the choir. Will the “passion choir” and Maestro Yim complete this impossible mission and win the competition?

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the club’s top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: Mr. Long
programme.desc: A Taiwanese hitman Mr. Long escapes from the triad after his assignment in Tokyo gone awry. He encounters a Taiwanese woman and her son and the three of them start a new life together. Unfortunately, Mr. Long is being pursued by the triad again…

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix’s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kit’s master, Debo.

programme.title: Twilight of the Warriors: Walled In
programme.desc: Young Chan Lok Kwun accidentally stumbles into the Kowloon Walled City while fleeing, subsequently finding purpose amid chaos and gaining wisdom. Bonding with Shin, Twelfth Master and AV, they unite under Tornado's leadership to defend against the villain, Mr Big's assaults, and pledge to protect the safe haven of the Walled City together.

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Shark Busters
programme.desc: During the financial crisis, a vast majority of Hong Kong people experience difficulties in repaying debts. During this time, loan sharks use ruthless ways to force debtors to repay their loans and it is up to Officer Lee and his underground team to hunt down the head of this illegal organization.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home; an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death; the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his family’s expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his family’s reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident…

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Choi’s actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: From Vegas To Macau
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as "Magic Hands" Ken, a legendary gambling maestro who is forced out of retirement when his daughter's safety is compromised by an international gambling mafia. In order to save her, Ken and his new protégé Cool must work together to expose the evil mastermind by challenging him to a high stakes head-to-head battle of cards.

programme.title: Sound of Colors
programme.desc: Lonesome marriage consultant Ming meets a blind but charming young lady, Yeuk, at a subway station. When Ming suddenly turns blind too, Yeuk helps him navigate through his world of darkness, and they begin to fall in love. This feature is based on the illustrated book from famous Taiwan illustrator Jimmy Liao.

Nasib mempertemukan tiga sekawan ini dengan Berta, wanita jadi-jadian yang berprofesi sebagai germo. Akhirnya ke tiga sekawan itu menerima dengan satu persyaratan: asal mereka tetap perawan.

programme.title: Membakar Matahari
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Yanti yang hidupnya berubah sejak diperkosa kawanan penjahat dan dijadikan pelacur di jakarta. Tetapi ia bisa diselamatkan oleh pacarnya, Rachman sebelum ia terjerumus lebih jauh. Walaupun Yanti bekas pelacur, Rachman tetap menikahinya. Setelah belajar ilmu bela diri dari kakeknya Rachman, Yanti dan Rachman memutuskan untuk balas dendam kepada penjahat yang telah memperkosa Yanti

programme.title: Mencari Hilal
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang Mahmud yang selalu ingin mengajarkan bahwa Islam itu adalah agama untuk semua persoalan hidup. Dalam perjalannya mencari hilal dengan caranya yang sederhana tanpa menelan biaya sampai milyaran rupiah yang selama ini dilakukan oleh pemerintah, langkahnya terhalang dengan anaknya bernama Heli. Heli selau melontarkan pikiran liberalnya hingga membuat Mahmud gerah.

programme.title: Kuntilanak 2 (2019)
programme.desc: Di film pertama, Dinda berhasil lolos dari teror kuntilanak. Ia kemudian berniat menemui Karmila yang diyakini sebagai ibu kandungnya. Sialnya, Dinda yang berangkat bersama adik dan temannya malah terjebak dalam rumah di tengah hutan. Kejanggalan mulai terjadi di rumah tersebut. Dinda harus kembali berhadapan dengan kuntilanak.

programme.title: Perempuan-Perempuan Liar
programme.desc: Dua penagih hutang sinting, Dom dan Mino, tak sengaja bertemu perempuan gila, Mey dan Cindy. Dom dan Mino terjebak permainan gila Mey dan Cindy. Mereka membawa kabur Mey dari pernikahan

programme.title: Soekarno
programme.desc: Soekarno berperan penting dalam kemerdekaan Indonesia, dengan dibantu sahabat-sahabatnya. Dalam kisah ini juga ada sosok perempuan yang selalu mendukung karir dari soekarno yaitu Inggit dan Fatmawati, konflik juga sempat terjadi dalam kisah asmara Soekarno. Hingga pada akhirnya Indonesia bisa merdeka pada tanggal 17 Agustus 1945 dengan ditandakan pembacaan proklamasi oleh Soekarno.

programme.title: Roy Kiyoshi (The Untold Story)
programme.desc: Roy, yang punya kemampuan berinteraksi dengan makhluk gaib sangat frustrasi ketika Rani adiknya diculik setan. Roy merasa gagal melindungi adiknya. Tiga tahun kemudian, Sheila, pekerja LSM yang peduli dalam penanggulangan anak hilang diteror setan ketika sedang menangani kasus anak hilang secara misterius. Sheila sangat yakin bahwa kemunculan setan ini ada hubungannya dengan kasus yang sedang ditanganinya.

programme.title: Hotline 666
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang Erza yang terperangkap di sebuah rumah angker. Erza merupakan pengantar pizza, saat dia mengantaran pizza ke sebuah rumah an ternyata dihuni oleh Sandra, Miko, dan Dara. Sosok yang awalnya hanyalah rekaan Erza menjadi nyata. Pintu rumah itu tertutup secara gaib. Erza terkunci di dalamnya.

programme.title: Pohon Keramat
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang keluarga yang diteror oleh hantu pohon besar yang ada di depan rumah baru mereka. Keganjilan demi keganjilan terus berlanjut dan selalu mengintai keluarga tersebut.

programme.title: Berangkat
programme.desc: Kisah tiga sekawan, yakni, Jano, Joana, dan Dika yang masing-masing memiliki personality dan hobi yang berbeda. Mereka melakukan road trip ke Kawah Ijen dan dilanjutkan ke Bali. Bermodalkan VW Combi tua mereka menyusuri beberapa kota di Jawa dengan banyak cerita.

programme.title: Skandal
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang seorang wanita yang selingkuh dengan kekasih lamanya karena merasa jenuh dengan kehidupan rumah tangganya. Dengan sifat posesif yang dimiliki kekasih lamanya, teror demi teror mulai diterima wanita itu dan keluarganya.

programme.title: Kirun+Adul Pengen Punya Pacar Keren
programme.desc: Anak perempuan Wakil Presiden diculik. Kirun dan Adul disinyalir jadi penjahatnya.

programme.title: Rumah Bekas Kuburan
programme.desc: Karina menyimpan masa lalu kelam: Larasati tidak sengaja terbunuh ketika Karina kepergok selingkuh dengan Danu, suami Larasati. Akibat kesalahan itu, Kirana harus memberikan tumbal pada arwah Larasati. Alhasil tiga suami Karina meninggal dan Larasati tetap menuntut tumbal.

programme.title: Boneka Dari Indiana
programme.desc: Film komedi yang menceritakan tentang seorang suami, Egy, yang berada di bawah kekuasaan istrinya, Cece, yang juga di bawah mertuanya, Yudho. Namun, ada hal yang membuat Egi akhirnya memberontak dan berhenti menjadi "boneka".

programme.title: Pelet Kuntilanak
programme.desc: Karena terobsesi dengan kecantikan dan juga untuk membalaskan dendam kepada pria-pria yang memperkosanya, Pamela dan juga Tantri bersekutu dengan iblis. Mereka pergi ke dukun dan menggunakan pelet celana dalam pria. Namun keadaan berubah ketika mereka berdua justru mengalami teror dari mahluk gaib yang menyerang mereka.

programme.title: Misteri Gunung Merapi
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang seorang pendekar, Sembara, yang diharuskan menuntut ilmu menjelajahi hutan jika ingin kekuatannya bertambah. Dengan sangat terpaksa ia meninggalkan kekasihnya, Farida. Ia berguru kepada manusia harimau. Saat selesai, ia mempunyai misi untuk membunuh manusia harimau lainnya yang haus darah, yaitu Mardia. Pada satu kesempatan, Sembara berhasil mengalahkannya.

programme.title: Cas Cis Cus
programme.desc: Bercerita tentang seorang nenek yang sepanjang cerita dicitrakan selalu marah-marah sebelum keinginannya dipenuhi, yaitu : Minta kaset video porno dan minta kawin lagi dengan tukang pijit langganannya. Bahkan ia sempat lari dari rumah, walaupun akhirnya kembali lagi.

programme.title: Senggol Bacok
programme.desc: Galang tempramental & tidak pernah takut apapun, namun ia harus mengendalikan emosinya untuk dapat memenangkan hati sang cewek idaman.

programme.title: Belahan Jiwa
programme.desc: Cerita tentang empat sahabat yang selalu setia bersama, dan ternyata mereka semua berhubungan dengan pria yang sama

programme.title: Cinta Tapi Beda
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang sepasang kekasih yang berbeda keyakinan Diana dan Cahyo. Namun saat mereka mulai mencoba melanjutkan ke jenjang yang lebih serius, orang tua mereka sangat bertentangan dengan rencana ini. Hingga dilema mereka memuncak saat Diana dijodohkan oleh Oka pria pilihan ibunya.

programme.title: Tiga
programme.desc: Menceritakan tentang masa depan di tahun 2036. Dikisahkan oleh tiga sahabat bernama Alif, Lam dan Mim yang ditemukan dengan situasi dimana mereka harus berjuangan atas kebenaran masing-masing.

programme.title: Si Manis Jembatan Ancol
programme.desc: Maryam, sosok perempuan yang mencari kebahagiaan saat rumah tangganya dengan lelaki bernama Roy berada di ambang kehancuran. Hadirnya sosok Yudha mampu membuat Maryam menemukan ketenangan. Namun, sebuah kejadian tragis harus menimpanya. Setelah itu legenda menyeramkan mulai tersebar.

programme.title: Ganesha
programme.desc: Ganesha, pemuda daerah yang mencoba mengadu nasib di kota, karena atas pengaruh temannya. Pada saat perjalanan, ia berhasil menggagalkan aksi pembajakan di bis yang ia tumpangi. Sang supir pun berterima kasih kepadanya dan mengangkatnya anak.

programme.title: Ricky Nakalnya Anak Muda
programme.desc: Ricky sangat terpukul dengan kematian pacarnya, Sita saat terjun payung. la jadi kacau, kerjanya cuma jalan-jalan dengan jip tua terbuka, kumpul-kumpul dengan gengnya, dan berkelahi.

programme.title: Pesan Dari Surga
programme.desc: Grup band beraliran rock, Topeng, yang seluruh personilnya beranggotakan lima anak muda, menghadapi berbagai problem cinta. Ketika permasalahan nyaris meledak, seorang korban kecelakaan yang selamat ini dalam kondisi koma tiba-tiba sadar dan membawa berbagai pesan dari surga.

programme.title: 5 Cowok Jagoan
programme.desc: Yanto adalah seorang cleaning service dari perusahaan obat ternama harus menyelamatkan kekasihnya, Dewi yang diculik oleh para segerombolan pasukan bersenjata dan profesional. Yanto meminta bantuan dari para keempat sahabatnya karena sejak kecil mereka saling berjanji untuk saling membantu apabila ada yang mengalami kesulitan. Mereka semua memiliki background berbeda-beda, Dedy adalah seorang hansip kampung, Danu seorang penipu ulung, Lilo seorang gamer dan ahli computer dan Reva seorang mantan preman. Dengan janji mereka tersebut, akhirnya Yanto dibantu keempat para sahabatnya serta seorang cewek jagoan juga bernama Debby.

programme.title: Ummi Aminah
programme.desc: Ummi Aminah, ustadzah 68 tahun, memiliki jamaah setia mencapai ribuan. Ummi memiliki tujuh anak dengan berbagai macam perbedaan sifatnya

programme.title: Kutukan Arwah Santet
programme.desc: Film ini bercerita tentang kisah terbunuhnya seorang gadis yang menyimpan misteri. Beberapa tahun setelah kematiannya, arwah gadis ini pun kerap merasuki tubuh Kirana dan menimbulkan korban. Suatu hari, penyebab kematian gadis ini pun terkuak.

programme.title: Melodi Cinta Rhoma Irama
programme.desc: Rhoma jatuh cinta dengan Ricca dan sempat merencanakan pernikahan. Namun jalinan cinta mereka diganggu oleh Herman yang juga mencintai Ricca dan ingin menguasai harta ayah Ricca

programme.title: Rumah Bekas Kuburan
programme.desc: Karina menyimpan masa lalu kelam: Larasati tidak sengaja terbunuh ketika Karina kepergok selingkuh dengan Danu, suami Larasati. Akibat kesalahan itu, Kirana harus memberikan tumbal pada arwah Larasati. Alhasil tiga suami Karina meninggal dan Larasati tetap menuntut tumbal.

programme.title: Arwah Goyang Jupe Depe
programme.desc: Lilis yang dulunya berprofesi sebagai penari disebuah grup tari jaipong, harus kembali ke profesi lamanya karena tuntutan ekonomi keluarga. Suaminya korban PHK dan menganggur. Namun, Neneng yang sekarang menjadi bintang primadona di grup tari tersebut, merasa mendapatkan saingan. Karena dengan cepat, pengunjung kembali menyukai Lilis. Persaingan anatara keduanya pun terjadi.

programme.title: Jangan Bilang Siapa-Siapa
programme.desc: Film ini menceritakan tentang Merry dan Andi yang baru menikah, namun sudah terjadi keanehan yang berujung kecurigaan di awal pernikahan mereka. Ditambah lagi saat Merry mendengar pembicaraan Andi dengan Kadir, pembantunya, dan akhirnya menjadi banyak salah paham.

programme.desc: 3 tahun di ibukota GUNADI masih juga menganggur, sementara Bapaknya meminta Lebaran tahun ini harus pulang kampung. 3 tahun pula, Lestari menunggu segera dinikahi dengan mas kawin berupa perlengkapan shalat, tunai!

programme.title: Issaq
programme.desc: The story is in Benaras, a town of India, and its neighbouring areas that are witness to violence unleashed by the sand mafia controlled by urban elite and equally violent retaliation by Naxalite armies. The sand mafia is run by two influential Banarasi families, Kashyaps and Mishras, who are brutal enemies. Kashyap has an 18-year-old, pretty and innocent daughter Bachchi from his first wife. On the other hand, Mishra's son Rahul (Played by Prateik) is a good-looking teenager with predictable interests for a boy of his background - Girls & Guns! Things change when the battle-hardened and pleasure-seeking Rahul, and the romantic yet head-strong Bachchi fall in love. Disregarding the consequences, the young lovers choose to go ahead with the dictats of their hearts. What follows is a high octane action-filled drama!
